{"tid":1465502,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"停你老母，擇善固執啊！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:29:57.000Z","uid":202076,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe24728b9f54f94c0efa7048f799119de512616","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n今日圍大陸公安一事，又出現連日講出嘅問題：對家想盡一切辦法分化我地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析：<br />\n<br />\n打9佢：比狗出師有名<br />\n唔打：對唔住一眾被捕手足<br />\n<br />\n阻人上機：印象減分<br />\n唔阻：航班唔會cancel<br />\n<br />\n繼續係公你贏，字我輸嘅局面，從而分化和理非勇武，唔好忘記塞機場係為咗揸撚住港共春袋，打經濟牌，上面冇一樣嘢爭贏咗or爭輸咗會改變「損失經濟」呢個事實，所以共狗只能夠不斷分化，減少出嚟嘅人數<br />\n<br />\n最後，唔好在意當刻嘅輸贏，只要件事係啱嘅，就好擇善固執，繼續塞撚爆機場。<br />\n<br />\n不分化講就易，麻煩大家屌對方之前停一停諗一諗，因為分化緊彼此嘅就係港共最想做嘅。"},{"pid":"b727b30b40002595e7f9a0e6aef2ea145a814a89","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64556e07049b1d85ae58de962093dd11b04e7482","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"a615aec9b277907c5228be0dd92bb1a4164262c2","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"1cb9a06652409f38a503e1881533fce26279d7d4","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"ec67d090e61e3e8ef867346bcced245f01fe0d0e","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"3994cc155db705d66db66ecda4675c4b44759178","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"a1ff44f0daad37bfca23b51500e3dd7909710808","tid":1465502,"uid":202076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"af5488ae5ca1a638364c9ba28fe933f2c38fdebe